mixin heroVideo()
  .homepage-hero-module
    .video-container
      .filter
      video.fillWidth(autoplay='', loop='')
        source(src='images/Outventure-landing-page.m4v', type='video/mp4')
        | Your browser does not support the video tag. I suggest you upgrade your browser.
        source(src='images/Outventure-landing-page.m4v', type='video/webm')
        | Your browser does not support the video tag. I suggest you upgrade your browser.
